room_title: Escape room "Boardwalk Blast" by Escape Garden State in New York
room_address: ​1275 Bloomfield Avenue - Unit 49 Building 7, Fairfield, NJ 07004
room_description:
​It is the last day of summer in New Jersey. You are enjoying a nice day on the Jersey Shore boardwalk when news breaks that authorities have ordered a mandatory evacuation. Reports indicate that a 'blast' may potentially go off somewhere inside the arcade.
Our team has been contacted to investigate the arcade and try to neutralize the threat. You have one hour to find the source of the reports and to enjoy all the fun the boardwalk has left to offer!
